{
  "stem": "6258.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow at this time, I was working in that Kranken-Revier in this like cleaning or hospital-- small hospital for the SS men.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for that-- they were people from Latvian and Ukrainian who were in SS uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not SS uniforms, but who were there with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there I was, just cleaning this-- I was the cleaning lady.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are the same, yes, barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at this time, I-- even before we went from the nachrichtengeratenlager, after this girl ran away, they brought us the striped jackets.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The striped clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Plaszow, it was also this terrible soup and-- and this terrible, well, so to speak, coffee, what was water, and a piece of bread and sometimes margarine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only once when there was a commission from the Red Cross, we got egg and something like sugar.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole camp was doing kogel-mogel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to ask them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I did not see them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was regularly, well, about 10 o'clock till 5:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were not hungry, because when we were working, everybody who was working with-- well, like-- like I was in this Kranken-Revier, and then they always let-- there was always bread and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were two-- one woman, Madame [NON-ENGLISH], she was working as a secretary, and I was a cleaning lady.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this time, in the Revier, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- of course, there was that mountain of where they do the execution in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were-- we-- it was very-- in full view from that roll call plat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ha!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What kind of a question is this?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
